TITLE: Example of Building Unsigned Transaction Using Polkadot.js API in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates the full process of importing necessary APIs, connecting to a Polkadot node, fetching latest block headers, constructing the method call, era, nonce, and finally assembling the unsigned transaction object with all required metadata. This snippet depends on '@polkadot/api' and assumes an existing 'keyring' and helper function for nonce retrieval.
SOURCE: https://github.com/reown-com/reown-docs/blob/main/advanced/multichain/polkadot/dapp-integration-guide.mdx#_snippet_6

