TITLE: Hashing Messages for EIP-1271 using web3.js in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to calculate an EIP-191 compliant message hash using the web3.js library. This hash is necessary when calling the `isValidSignature` method specified by EIP-1271 to validate signatures originating from smart contract wallets. Requires the `web3` library and an RPC URL.
SOURCE: https://github.com/reown-com/reown-docs/blob/main/advanced/api/sign/smart-contract-wallet-usage.mdx#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
