TITLE: Creating AuthRequestParams Extension with Default Values
DESCRIPTION: Example implementation of an extension for AuthRequestParams that provides default values for SIWE message creation. This includes domain, chains, nonce, URI, statement, resources for ReCaps, and methods.
SOURCE: https://github.com/reown-com/reown-docs/blob/main/appkit/ios/core/one-click-auth.mdx#_snippet_1

