DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to extend WalletConnect functionality by defining a custom method (`polkadot_getSignedHex`) in the session namespace and providing its implementation in the wallet's codebase (TypeScript example shown). The example shows adding the method to the `methods` array in the namespace definition and includes a sample `getSignedHex` function that signs a payload and returns the transaction hex.
