TITLE: Initializing React AppKit with Bitcoin Adapter and Configuration (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet sets up the main configuration for integrating Bitcoin wallets into a React application using Reown's AppKit. It involves importing necessary libraries, defining project info, network settings, and creating the app with specified adapters and features. The configuration functions are called outside of React components to optimize rerendering behavior.
