TITLE: Connecting with WalletConnect Modal - Android Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to initiate a connection using the WalletConnect Modal SDK in Android Kotlin. It shows how to prepare the required and optional namespaces and call the `WalletConnectModal.connect` function with success and error callbacks.
