TITLE: Implementing Message Signing for SIWE Authentication
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement a message signing function for SIWE authentication using Web3 SPM package. Creates a signature using the provided private key and MessageSignerFactory.
SOURCE: https://github.com/reown-com/reown-docs/blob/main/walletkit/ios/notifications/notify/usage.mdx#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: swift
CODE:
```
func onSign(message: String) -> CacaoSignature {
    let privateKey = Data(hex: privateKey)
    let signer = MessageSignerFactory(signerFactory: DefaultSignerFactory()).create()
    let signature = try! signer.sign(message: message, privateKey: privateKey, type: .eip191)
    return signature
}
```

