TITLE: Creating WalletConnect Notify Subscription (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to initiate a new notification subscription for an account to a specific dapp using `notifyClient.subscribe()`. It requires the target account address and the domain of the dapp to subscribe to. The result is reflected via the previously registered `notify_update` and `notify_subscriptions_changed` events.
